Package org.daisy.streamline.api.tasks

Class ReadOnlyTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.streamline.api.tasks.InternalTask
      • org.daisy.streamline.api.tasks.ReadOnlyTask
  • public abstract class ReadOnlyTask
extends InternalTask
    Provides an abstract base for read only tasks. A read only task is a task that does not produce an altered output.
